name: Senior #7 - Chang
description:
Chang is a 76-year-old former golf caddy who enjoys reading, binge-watching Korean dramas and vandalising mailboxes. He is loveable and pleasant, but can also be very sneaky and a bit manipulative.

He is addicted to strawberry bonbons, something which his friend Anne pointed out when he was 18. The problem intensified in 1963. Chang has lost three jobs as a result of his addiction, specifically: dishwasher at burger joint, local activist and movie extra.
